# OceanView Resort — UML Diagrams

> All diagrams are derived directly from the project source code (`src/java/model`, `dao`, `servlet`) and `schema.sql`.

---

## 1. Class Diagram

Shows all classes, their fields, methods, and relationships.

```mermaid
classDiagram
    direction TB

    %% ─── MODEL LAYER ───────────────────────────────────────
    class User {
        -int userId
        -String firstName
        -String lastName
        -String email
        -String password
        -String phone
        -String address
        -String nicPassport
        +getUserId() int
        +getFirstName() String
        +getLastName() String
        +getEmail() String
        +getPhone() String
        +getAddress() String
        +getNicPassport() String
    }

    class Staff {
        -int id
        -String username
        -String fullName
        -String email
        -String role
        +getId() int
        +getUsername() String
        +getFullName() String
        +getEmail() String
        +getRole() String
    }

    class Room {
        -int roomId
        -String roomNumber
        -String type
        -double price
        -String status
        -String description
        +getRoomId() int
        +getRoomNumber() String
        +getType() String
        +getPrice() double
        +getStatus() String
    }

    class Booking {
        -int bookingId
        -int guestId
        -int roomId
        -Date checkIn
        -Date checkOut
        -double totalPrice
        -String status
        -String guestName
        -String guestEmail
        -String roomNumber
        +getBookingId() int
        +getGuestId() int
        +getRoomId() int
        +getCheckIn() Date
        +getCheckOut() Date
        +getTotalPrice() double
        +getStatus() String
    }

    class Payment {
        -int paymentId
        -int bookingId
        -String paymentMethod
        -double amount
        -String paymentStatus
        -Timestamp paymentDate
        +getPaymentId() int
        +getBookingId() int
        +getPaymentMethod() String
        +getAmount() double
        +getPaymentStatus() String
        +getPaymentDate() Timestamp
    }

    %% ─── DAO LAYER ──────────────────────────────────────────
    class DBConnection {
        -static DBConnection instance
        -Connection connection
        +getInstance() DBConnection
        +getConnection() Connection
    }

    class StaffDAO {
        +authenticate(email, password) Staff
        +getAllStaff() List~Staff~
        +addStaff(Staff) boolean
        +deleteStaff(id) boolean
    }

    class UserDAO {
        +addUser(User) boolean
        +getAllUsers() List~User~
        +getUserById(id) User
    }

    class RoomDAO {
        +getAllRooms() List~Room~
        +searchRooms(number, type, status) List~Room~
        +getRoomById(id) Room
        +addRoom(Room) boolean
        +updateRoom(Room) boolean
        +deleteRoom(id) boolean
        +getRoomCount() int
        +getCountByStatus(status) int
    }

    class BookingDAO {
        +getAllBookings() List~Booking~
        +addBooking(Booking) boolean
        +updateBookingStatus(id, status) boolean
        +deleteBooking(id) boolean
        +getBookingById(id) Booking
        +getActiveBookingCount() int
        +getTotalRevenue() double
        +getMonthlyRevenue() List~JSONObject~
        +getCancellationStats() JSONObject
    }

    class PaymentDAO {
        +addPayment(Payment) boolean
        +getAllPayments() List~Payment~
        +getPaymentByBookingId(id) Payment
    }

    %% ─── SERVLET LAYER ──────────────────────────────────────
    class LoginServlet {
        -StaffDAO staffDAO
        +doGet(req, res) void
        +doPost(req, res) void
    }

    class RoomServlet {
        -RoomDAO roomDAO
        +doGet(req, res) void
        +doPost(req, res) void
    }

    class BookingServlet {
        -BookingDAO bookingDAO
        +doGet(req, res) void
        +doPost(req, res) void
    }

    class PaymentServlet {
        -PaymentDAO paymentDAO
        -BookingDAO bookingDAO
        +doGet(req, res) void
        +doPost(req, res) void
    }

    class UserServlet {
        -UserDAO userDAO
        +doGet(req, res) void
        +doPost(req, res) void
    }

    class DashboardServlet {
        -RoomDAO roomDAO
        -BookingDAO bookingDAO
        +doGet(req, res) void
    }

    class AuthFilter {
        +doFilter(req, res, chain) void
    }

    class LogoutServlet {
        +doGet(req, res) void
    }

    %% ─── RELATIONSHIPS ──────────────────────────────────────
    Booking "many" --> "1" User : guestId
    Booking "many" --> "1" Room : roomId
    Payment "1" --> "1" Booking : bookingId

    BookingDAO ..> Booking : uses
    BookingDAO ..> DBConnection : uses
    PaymentDAO ..> Payment : uses
    PaymentDAO ..> DBConnection : uses
    RoomDAO ..> Room : uses
    RoomDAO ..> DBConnection : uses
    UserDAO ..> User : uses
    UserDAO ..> DBConnection : uses
    StaffDAO ..> Staff : uses
    StaffDAO ..> DBConnection : uses

    LoginServlet --> StaffDAO : delegates
    RoomServlet --> RoomDAO : delegates
    BookingServlet --> BookingDAO : delegates
    PaymentServlet --> PaymentDAO : delegates
    PaymentServlet --> BookingDAO : delegates
    UserServlet --> UserDAO : delegates
    DashboardServlet --> RoomDAO : delegates
    DashboardServlet --> BookingDAO : delegates
    AuthFilter ..> LoginServlet : protects routes
```

